verbose_text: Accordingly, RT-qPCR and WB analysis revealed that upregulated miR-346 could increase the expression levels of TIMP-1 and TIMP-2, although the expression levels of MMP-2 and MMP-9 in the two cell lines were decreased, and these results showed the opposite trend to those performed with downregulated miR-346 (P < 0.05; XREF_FIG).
